{"name": "iterative-telemetry", "metadata": {"name": "iterative-telemetry", "version": "0.0.9", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/iterative/telemetry-python", "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests", "appdirs", "filelock", "distro"], "summary": "Common library for sending telemetry", "upload_time": 1726545296}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  Black: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg\n    :alt: Black\n    :target: https://github.com/psf/black\n    ```\n  Codecov: |-\n    ```{image} https://codecov.io/gh/iterative/iterative-telemetry/branch/main/graph/badge.svg\n    :alt: Codecov\n    :target: https://app.codecov.io/gh/iterative/iterative-telemetry\n    ```\n  License: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/iterative-telemetry\n    :alt: License\n    :target: https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0\n    ```\n  PyPI: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/iterative-telemetry.svg\n    :alt: PyPI\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/iterative-telemetry/\n    ```\n  Python Version: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/iterative-telemetry\n    :alt: Python Version\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/iterative-telemetry\n    ```\n  Status: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/status/iterative-telemetry.svg\n    :alt: Status\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/iterative-telemetry/\n    ```\n  Tests: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/iterative/iterative-telemetry/workflows/Tests/badge.svg\n    :alt: Tests\n    :target: https://github.com/iterative/iterative-telemetry/actions?workflow=Tests\n    ```\n  pre-commit: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/pre--commit-enabled-brightgreen?logo=pre-commit&logoColor=white\n    :alt: pre-commit\n    :target: https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit\n    ```\n---\n\n# Iterative Telemetry\n\n{{ PyPI }} {{ Status }} {{ Python Version }} {{ License }}\n\n{{ Tests }} {{ Codecov }} {{ pre-commit }} {{ Black }}\n\n## Features\n\n- can be disabled in all tools by setting `ITERATIVE_DO_NOT_TRACK=1` env var\n- single anonymised `user_id` across all `iterative` projects\n- collects minimal amount of anonymised data. For example:\n\n```python\n{\n    \"tool_name\": \"dvc\",\n    \"tool_version\": \"2.14.0\",\n    \"user_id\": \"e798d2e2-8941-4f24-a868-3adcbf6467df\",\n    \"os_name\": \"mac\",\n    \"os_version\": \"12.3\",\n}\n```\n\n## Requirements\n\n- TODO\n\n## Installation\n\nYou can install *Iterative Telemetry* via [pip] from [PyPI]:\n\n```console\n$ pip install iterative-telemetry\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n## Contributing\n\nContributions are very welcome.\nTo learn more, see the [Contributor Guide].\n\n## License\n\nDistributed under the terms of the [Apache 2.0 license],\n*Iterative Telemetry* is free and open source software.\n\n## Issues\n\nIf you encounter any problems,\nplease [file an issue] along with a detailed description.\n\n% github-only\n\n[apache 2.0 license]: https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0\n[contributor guide]: CONTRIBUTING.rst\n[file an issue]: https://github.com/iterative/iterative-telemetry/issues\n[pip]: https://pip.pypa.io/\n[pypi]: https://pypi.org/\n"], "modules": [{"name": "iterative_telemetry", "documentation": ["Iterative Telemetry."], "functions": [{"name": "iterative_telemetry._system_info", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["A randomly generated ID string"]}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry.ci_id_generator", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "func", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_github_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["group_id = \"$GITHUB_SERVER_URL/$(dirname \"$GITHUB_REPOSITORY\")\"\nuser_id = \"$(gh api users/$GITHUB_ACTOR --jq '.name, .login, .id' |\n             xargs echo)"]}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_gitlab_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["group_id = \"$CI_SERVER_URL/$CI_PROJECT_ROOT_NAMESPACE\"\nuser_id = \"$GITLAB_USER_NAME $GITLAB_USER_LOGIN $GITLAB_USER_ID"]}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_bitbucket_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["group_id = \"$BITBUCKET_WORKSPACE\"\nuser_id = \"$(git log -1 --pretty=format:'%ae')"]}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_generic_ci_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._generate_ci_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._read_user_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "config_file", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry._read_user_id_locked", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "config_file", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry.find_or_create_user_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["The user's ID is stored on a file under the global config directory.\nThe file should contain a JSON with a \"user_id\" key:\n    {\"user_id\": \"16fd2706-8baf-433b-82eb-8c7fada847da\"}\nIDs are generated randomly with UUID4."]}, {"name": "iterative_telemetry.deterministic", "asynchronou